The paper presents an approach to learning a type of hidden Markov model (HMM) for regression, which involves inferring the structure and parameters of a conventional HMM while simultaneously learning a regression model. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SD (Sound), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
